1) In a launch file run tf_remapper

    <node pkg="tf" type="tf_remap" name="tf_remapper" output="screen">
    <rosparam param="mappings">
    [{old: betaX/base_link, new: base_link}]
    </rosparam>
    </node>
    
2) Spawm urdf file in factory

3) export LIBGL_ALWAYS_SOFTWARE=1


4) Run Rviz


5)rosbag play <bag_file> use_sim_time:=true tf:=tf_old


6) FOr converting Kazam recorded files for WIndows:

ffmpeg -i in.mp4 -pix_fmt yuv420p -c:a copy -movflags +faststart out.mp4
